title: Patty Duke Pulls Twin Tricks On Liv & Maddie Tonight!
text: Patty Duke Pulls Twin Tricks On Liv & Maddie Tonight! Sunday, 25 October 2015 (9 minutes ago) Maddie (Dove Cameron) and Grandma Janice (Patty Duke) plug up their noses in this fun new still from tonight’s Liv and Maddie. In “Grandma-A-Rooney”, Grandma Janice shows up to present Liv (also Cameron) with an award, but something just doesn’t feel right. Meanwhile, Joey (Joey Bragg) invites three girls over to watch the “Lover’s Comet.” [...]
